    {
      "Text": "The GNU mailing list manager.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nIn GNU Mailman before 2.1.38, a list member or moderator can get a CSRF token and craft an admin request (using that token) to set a new admin password or make other changes.(CVE-2021-44227)",
      "Title": "Description",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
